snippet.title: High Rise for the Apple II
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

Atari 8-bit



Game description:

High Rise is a puzzle game, in which you have to build carefully planned constructions, so that your builder can climb the top and reach the ladder.


What I think:

Quite fun puzzle game, but also quite repetitive.
